{"tid":1743521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，我地無分化既本錢","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:32:13.000Z","uid":57674,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2af37263044fba607ca53d9622de08f1af4be341","tid":1743521,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"我明好多人話泛民呢樣個樣<br />\n但係唔該 你真係忍心望住建制贏一個又一個既議席咩<br />\n我好唔讚成血債票償 但今次呢舊饅頭我地要食鳩梗<br />\n麻煩各位星期日 一早就起身去投票唔好懶<br />\n你幾唔鍾意泛民都好 總好過建制／空票 當我求求大家<br />\n我地已經無本錢可以分得咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住，730就去投，唔好俾對家搞事搞到要腰斬投票</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"63b9b99ecf9e7e1d0b12f5d3e0a557435b2ca57f","tid":1743521,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=9e493105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=e6401a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"htt